      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――東京　ライブ会場",
      "startTime": 0.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEでしたー！",
      "startTime": 3.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1233.3333333333335,
          "startTime": 4.533333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "またどこかで会えんの楽しみにしてますー！\n気を付けて帰ってな～",
      "startTime": 9.683333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなーアンコール、ありがとう～！\nうちも今日はめっちゃ楽しかったわぁ！",
      "startTime": 18.31666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "まだまだ歌いたいのに\nあっという間に終わるんやもん",
      "startTime": 24.245786212739496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それもこれも\n今日のライブが充実してたからやろな～",
      "startTime": 28.512452879406165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまみんなのおかげやわぁ！",
      "startTime": 31.67911954607283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（歌やダンスは当然ながら、MCや盛り上げ方に）\n（至るまで、相変わらず完成度が高い……）",
      "startTime": 38.61245287940616,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 34.74578621273949
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（中でも鈴村優の存在は大きいな。うちの子がここまで）\n（場の雰囲気を読んで喋るには、まだ場数が必要か）",
      "startTime": 46.712452879406165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなら瑠依ちゃん、すみれちゃん\nラスト一曲楽しんでいきましょ～",
      "startTime": 53.84578621273948,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.333333333343,
          "startTime": 56.679119546072826
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 61.179119546072826
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 61.179119546072826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ後　駅への道",
      "startTime": 61.345786212739505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（ライバルの偵察を終えた俺は、晩御飯を食べ）\n（そそくさと駅へ向かっていた）",
      "startTime": 67.71245287940611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 69.9124528794061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん",
      "startTime": 69.9124528794061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 71.45345062301267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……鈴村さん？　こんな所で会うなんて\nすごい偶然もあったものですね……",
      "startTime": 77.18678395634599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、せやね\n……でも、ほんとに偶然やろか？",
      "startTime": 82.25345062301265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 84.886783956346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ついさっきのことなんやけど、ここで\nうちらTRINITYAiLEのライブがあったんよ",
      "startTime": 87.75345062301267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだったんですか\n俺は……たまたま仕事で来ていて",
      "startTime": 94.086783956346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 97.68678395634599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "ふうん、たまたまねぇ",
      "startTime": 97.686783956346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 101.15426700001666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ところで{user}さん\nアンコールで歌った曲、どうでした？",
      "startTime": 102.98760033335004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、鈴村さんのMCから入った曲ですよね？\nとてもいい曲だと……あっ",
      "startTime": 110.14845177684904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 112.64845177684904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっいい曲って言ってもらえて嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 112.64845177684904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "それより、{user}さん\nもう帰るんです？",
      "startTime": 118.81806626672228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 120.5073633524389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく会ったんやし\nこの辺を案内してもらおう思ってたんですけど",
      "startTime": 122.24069668577222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "案内？　どうして俺が……",
      "startTime": 125.6406966857722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 128.64069668577218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、{user}さんは\n案内してくれはります",
      "startTime": 130.60736335243888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 132.6139590676714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "だって、はるばる東京まで来て\nうちらのライブを熱心に偵察しはって……",
      "startTime": 135.68062573433832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "偵察された当の本人がこうしてお願いしてるんやから\n……断るはずないやろ～？",
      "startTime": 143.9472924010051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 146.38062573433842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……俺はどこを案内すればいいんでしょうか\n……わかりました",
      "startTime": 146.38062573433842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、{user}さんの気が\n変わってくれて良かったです",
      "startTime": 153.6806257343384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 156.2802889036341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、お言葉に甘えて\nあのお店を案内してもらおうかなぁ",
      "startTime": 158.9136222369675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 162.0802889036342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あれは……アニメグッズや、漫画、小説なんかを\n取り扱っているアニメショップですね",
      "startTime": 166.11362223696764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 168.48028890363432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "へえ～、そうなんやね……",
      "startTime": 168.48028890363432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 171.3136903452084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "入ってみますか？　俺も買いたい漫画がありますし\nあ……でも、鈴村さんだとバレたら大変ですよね",
